Revision history for Class::Mite

v0.1.1  2026-04-14
        - Set no index for Class, Role, Class::More and Class::Clone.
        - Only provides Class::Mite now, all other modules are
          still available internally but not searchable on CPAN.

v0.1.0  2026-04-14
        - Released to CPAN world.
        - Switched to dotted-decimal versioning (v-strings).

0.06  2025-10-23
      - Added test for DOES/does in Class.
      - Clean up export list in Class.

0.05  2025-10-17
      - Support role composition

0.04  2025-10-14
      - Role now 'has' function

0.03  2025-10-14
      - Added Class::More support 'has'
      - Added Class::Clone support native clone()

0.02  2025-10-03
      - Added support for key 'extends' in Class.pm.

0.01  2025-10-02
      - Module Created.
